mapper.insert: INSERT INTO member_info (personalId, memberUuid, name, email, birthDay,phoneNumber, gender, content, address, education, experience, skills, awards,registrarId, registrarDatetime, modifierId, modifierDatetime) VALUES (#{personalId}, #{memberUuid}, #{name}, #{email}, #{birthDay}, #{phoneNumber}, #{gender}, #{content}, #{address}, #{education}, #{experience}, #{skills}, #{awards}, #{registrarId}, #{registrarDatetime}, #{modifierId}, #{modifierDatetime})
